data.description: Charming home with three bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms sitting on a nice size corner lot. Some of the upgrades include roof and exterior paint in 2021. Original hardwood floors, nice size bedrooms and an EAT-IN kitchen area. Living area has built in shelving with updated light fixtures throughout the home. Laundry hookups are in garage. Easy to show! Bring your vision to this home and make it your own.
